author: Hondo
title: Hondo pays with Jays
text:
Hondo, riding high with a sweep on Monday, was shut down on Tuesday when Dickey and the dreadful Jays were steamrolled by the Royals to raise the debt to 1,837 stones. 
Wednesday: Mr. Aitch expects the Small Bears to claw their way past Matz and the Metamucils — 20 units on Hammel.
Joe Biden changed his story Tuesday on whether he advised Obama to proceed with the Osama bin Laden mission. Having said in 2012 he told the President, “Don’t go,” the VP now claims he told Obama in private he should go after him. Don’t be too hard on the Gaffe Machine; if he’s going to run for President, he’s going to have to be ready to flip-flop and lie at all times just to keep up with Hillary. … Oprah reportedly invested $43.2 million in Weight Watchers. She’s obviously a big believer in the company, but even if it doesn’t help her with her poundage problem, she at least will have a lot less money to spend at the grocery store.
